{
  "_comment": "Composed HEAVY PostgreSQL window (crud_filter=gen-heavy-pg) — owner approvals 2026-06-13. gen-heavy-pg-replica: origin+replica (two billable clusters, ~60-90min) with the same-region replica chain ending in the irreversible promote; run in a DEDICATED heavy window, not mixed with other heavy DB chains (2 PG clusters + their VPC). gen-heavy-pg-restore / gen-heavy-pg-upgrade are composed but DISABLED behind documented gates (backup timing / kernel-patchable precondition) — see _disabled_reason on each.",
